ram.com/creative_opts\">@creative_opts</a> &amp; <a href=\"http://instagram.com/amytangerine\">@amytangerine</a> and using the hashtag #creativeoptions for the chance to win the latest products from Creative Options! Be sure to also Like <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/creativeoptionscrafts\">Creative Options on Facebook</a> for more details. Contest ends tonight!</p>"
